{"tid":1070,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"將大家嘅故事 寫成一段段觸動人心嘅歌詞","createTime":"2016-11-25T15:47:27.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-27T16:06:00.000Z","uid":7401,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dac61fd7e49aef89c1330c96fdd06cd8ee6601b3","tid":1070,"uid":7401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T15:47:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcVaVCsMo32UJZniP2VWVare7zaz2FqkiQSLMiETukQtT?filename=qM81i5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqM81i5.jpg&h=8a60917c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家好，好開心黎到LIHK見到各位巴絲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能您地會話我係呢度promote<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係我嘅願望的確係希望可以做到大家嘅 甜詞人<br />\n係呢個Page上面，我地希望可以收到大家嘅故事，無論係同男女神暗示、示愛、箍煲、甚至離離合合嘅故事，我地都希望可以以我地rewrite嘅歌詞，一筆一劃自製嘅圖畫，將大家嘅故事一一收納係呢個Page入面。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家嘅一個微笑，一下點頭讚同，甚至每滴眼淚，都係對甜詞人嘅一份讚賞、認同。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後，希望大家多多支持、多多指教。<br />\n<br />\n甜詞人sweetlyricist<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/sweetlyricist\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsweetlyricist&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOV8W%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=38bc137e\" target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/sweetlyricist</a>"},{"pid":"34a41f069c07310dabd7e8f51bc636d8936c4f9e","tid":1070,"uid":7401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T16:04:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af147d5b593e0be615f3e67cc5f77b98d18ca1f4","tid":1070,"uid":7401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T16:21:28.000Z","msg":"希望大家多多支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黎緊好快就會岀新一份作品"},{"pid":"401dc75e003d3707bfac605657c7cad57e6bdd02","tid":1070,"uid":7401,"like":0,"dislike"